                    <Paragraph>
                        <Italic>Explanation of example</Italic> - Minimize IdealAutomate. Launch Notepad. Write intCounter to Notepad. If intCounter is less than 3, add 1 to intCounter and go to label loop. When intCounter is greater than 3, script will end.
